/ Make App Interface

%div#homeimprovement
  %div.title
    %h1
      H.I. with Monnie Bennett
      %div.content
        %div#categories
          %ul#category-list
            - @listing.each do |item|
              %li
                %a{:href => "/homeimprovement/#{item.to_a[0].to_a[1].gsub(' ', '%20')}"}=item.to_a[0].to_a[1]
        %div#category-stats

/ Templates

